text:
This outfit, the staff praised it a lot,
saying it suits me well...!

Oh, is that so?
That's great.

Yes...!
They said it suits me...

Since it was made thinking
it would suit Haruki...

As expected of you, Producer-san.
You really understand me, don't you...!
Ah, well, I'm Haruki's producer, after all.

Hehe... I'm glad you're the producer,
Producer-san...
